{"tid":821690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈山竹已經係回歸最強颱風","createTime":"2018-09-16T04:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T04:34:32.000Z","uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee781a853ce9575b4fa96d2ccc5b213a84df466","tid":821690,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"距離超過100公里已經令橫瀾島 (仲創紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )同青洲颶風<br />\n暴風8中3，颶風8中1而且仲有大幅上升嘅空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為未轉東南風<br />\n大美督船灣一帶更高達145<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/123015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F123015_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=43cf49d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山竹不但已係回歸最強，而且仲有能力挑戰溫黛荷貝愛倫等頂級10號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}